## Project Structure

```text
app/          ← unified Python service (FastAPI + SQLAlchemy + opensearch-py + AI/ML)
migrations/   ← golang-migrate SQL files (existing, keep as-is)
opensearch/   ← index mapping JSON + init.sh
scripts/      ← reindex_products.go, snapshot_seed.sql, search_relevance_check.sh
```

## Commands

```bash
# Run app locally
cd app && uv pip install -r requirements.txt
uvicorn main:app --host 0.0.0.0 --port 8080 --reload

# Lint / format
ruff check app/
ruff format app/

# Tests
pytest app/tests/
```

## Code Style

Python 3.11: follow PEP 8, use `ruff` for lint/format, `snake_case` for files and functions, `PascalCase` for classes and SQLAlchemy models, `PascalCase` + suffix for Pydantic schemas (e.g. `ProductResponse`).

